            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">51.104</ph> Furnishing assistance to contractors.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <p class="- topic/p ">After receiving an activity address code, the contracting officer will notify the appropriate GSA regional office or military activity, which will contact the contractor and-</p>
			      <ol id="d2996e16" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3010e20" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Provide initial copies of ordering information and instructions; and</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3010e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            When necessary, assist the contractor in preparing and submitting, as appropriate-</p>
					          <ol id="d2996e35" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3010e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The initial FEDSTRIP or MILSTRIP requisitions, the <xref href="https://www.gsa.gov/forms-library/order-supplies-and-services-0"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Optional Form 347</xref>, or the agency-approved forms;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3010e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A completed GSA Form 457, FSS Publications Mailing List Application, so that the contractor will automatically receive current copies of required publications; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3010e60" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A completed GSA Form 3525, Application for Customer Supply Center Services and (Address Change).</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
